        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="rounded-lg bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Jeune 2</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Culpa sit rerum incidunt, a consequuntur recusandae ab saepe illo est quia obcaecati neque quibusdam eius accusamus error officiis atque voluptates magnam!</p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="rounded-lg bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Jeune 3</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Culpa sit rerum incidunt, a consequuntur recusandae ab saepe illo est quia obcaecati neque quibusdam eius accusamus error officiis atque voluptates magnam!</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row mt-auto lg:h-64">
      <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-2/3 relative h-96 lg:h-full">
        <iframe title="Google Map" class="w-full h-full" loading="lazy" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2807.5984431230822!2d-71.88831392326924!3d45.27612747107143!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4cb651e9243c96f1%3A0xe598b3d3ea4d0f0!2sMaison%20des%20Jeunes%20de%20Waterville!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sca!4v1728844817897!5m2!1sfr!2sca"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/3 sm:flex-row flex items-center justify-center text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="lg:hidden flex flex-col m-4">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Venez nous voir</span>
            <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/Bts8i7Gb7xxub8NT6" class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 dark:text-white hover:text-gray-700/75 dark:hover:text-white/75">200 Rue du Dépôt, Waterville, QC</a>
          </p>
          <p class="flex flex-col m-4">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Appelez-nous</span>
            <a href="tel:+18194083103" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-gray-700 dark:text-white hover:text-gray-700/75 dark:hover:text-white/75">(819) 408-3103</a>
          </p>
          <ul class="m-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
